賣竉物既地方為左慳錢做埋好多仆街野, 唔好助長佢地"},{"pid":"8219ba2c408406c7b8686a6e0ec2732a5ab2e838","tid":1757210,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"諗清楚先好領養<br />\n<br />\nby the way <br />\n<br />\n借位宣傳下個app<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票吧！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1733465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1733465</a>"},{"pid":"812311de9ca96bfbb61a114f1221e074ca9cee9d","tid":1757210,"uid":197393,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"既然你都認為領養嘅狗唔可愛就唔好領養，買啦<br />\n養狗要照顧佢一世，揀隻自己真心鍾意嘅好重要<br />\n你夾硬因為人道揀隻冇咁可愛嘅狗返去<br />\n係咪確保你會全心全意對佢？<br />\n唔鍾意嘅夾硬要都冇意思 分分鐘搞到隻狗要俾人領養多次"},{"pid":"8215d09238064f96ed301e2fe8205017ccffd77e","tid":1757210,"uid":84581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7377b2757afe0e0554adff2840051952ab4a3d3a","tid":1757210,"uid":308450,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"其實隻小動物得唔得意係睇主人點養 見過好多一樣品種係唔同人手上可以好兩極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋好睇眼緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"見過領養主人養得好 d動物好食好住幾個月後會變樣  毛色靚又fluffy 開心活躣<br />\n<br />\n有d買番黎養得唔好 毛又唔梳 廁所又唔打理 餵d雜糧又差 長期落去有病又唔睇醫生 再衰d就拋棄"},{"pid":"b4688fbddc40fcea19d0347b85c2373e77901a1b","tid":1757210,"uid":309683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"唔好咁先入為主住先<br />\n<br />\n去下領養page睇下相先<br />\n有啲都好得意、好精靈<br />\n中型犬都有得揀<br />\n<br />\n甚至你話柴犬<br />\n因為柴柴好難教<br />\n有唔少柴因為有好多行為問題<br />\n俾人棄養<br />\n睇下你有無心教返好佢哋<br />\n多數係成犬<br />\n<br />\n你買嘅柴B，佢好大機會嚟自好細好細嘅生銹竉<br />\n阿媽生完一胎又生一胎，<br />\n因為地方太細腳、皮膚爛哂<br />\n你變相支持就有更多柴犬受害<br />\n<br />\n當然如果你去外國嗰種farm，親自探視個環境，買完運過嚟可能避免到以上情況，畢竟人係好自私嘅動物<br />\n不過普通香港人好難做到<br />\n<br />\n無得一句講哂<br />\n養竉物係要承諾佢一生<br />\n你要自己諗你隻狗唔係柴<br />\n你會唔會愛佢？照餵靚狗糧、陪佢玩，俾最好嘅佢<br />\n如果做唔到，堅持要買，<br />\n都好過你領養完佢唔愛佢嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登狗好得意"},{"pid":"d7a7c0f4840674e177e7f5c3b820c69a2c58b6a4","tid":1757210,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0afoWs7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0afoWs7.jpg&h=34a060e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"604e828170fc9726d5f2b3640dabccaee4801796","tid":1757210,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:37:13.000Z","msg":"下 我睇開個d領養page隻隻都好可愛"},{"pid":"5044c026de2c6ef7ce8baeecda06db70e9835a4a","tid":1757210,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T20:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8t5XrJf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8t5XrJf.png&h=2b92f823&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"463b1e1f807033c80debbe5ef0179377dcf44d2b","tid":1757210,"uid":20882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T20:18:53.000Z","msg":"唔需要為咗拎光環迫自己領養<br />\n最緊要合眼緣<br />\n當然唔好幫襯無良寵物店"},{"pid":"38e6714ad96e3421d7b625432f8407b7e7627f30","tid":1757210,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T20:19:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e1771d7973fa6d9def4e8a08a98b76ca4e4ed10","tid":1757210,"uid":236459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T20:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SceQMSd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSceQMSd.png&h=bd8ba20e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寵物店好多病貓病狗"},{"pid":"e57463b3c35c162bb862eba9315565eeadbc310d","tid":1757210,"uid":313312,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f820c7634f170ed92833bbee9591b75179dcd862","tid":1757210,"uid":156298,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"91f4ab7d307d8081